Acknowledgements

XenoDesign1's iterative hallucination design loop was conceptually inspired by
BoltzDesign1 (Cho et al.), though it shares none of its code and uses Chai-1 as
the structure model rather than Boltz. It builds on these external tools and
models, each under its own license: Chai-1, LigandMPNN/ProteinMPNN, CARBonAra,
ESM-2, PepMLM, and MetalHawk. Please cite the respective works when using the
corresponding components.
